## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="48b11-242">O tempo padrão é UTC.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="48b11-242">The time will default to UTC.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="48b11-243">Se você quiser especificar a hora em hora local, em seguida, especifique o <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> propriedade do `time` do objeto como <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="48b11-243">If you want to specify the time in local time, then specify the <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> property of the `time` object as <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="48b11-244">O código a seguir conecta-se à instância do ADAM hospedada pelo servidor de "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" no número de porta "5000".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="48b11-244">The following code connects to the ADAM instance hosted by the server "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" on port number "5000."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="48b11-245">O nome de usuário (adamAdmin) e a senha (SecretPwd123) são especificadas no <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> construtor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="48b11-245">The username (adamAdmin), and password (SecretPwd123) are specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="48b11-246">Uma pesquisa é executada para todas as entidades autenticáveis sob o contêiner "DC = adamApp1, DC = fabrikam, DC = com" que não fez logon com essa instância do ADAM nos últimos 45 dias.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="48b11-246">A search is performed for all authenticable principals under the container "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com" that have not logged on to this ADAM instance for the last 45 days.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="48b11-247">As entidades retornadas pela pesquisa, em seguida, são excluídas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="48b11-247">The principals returned by the search are then deleted.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                      ContextType.ApplicationDirectory,   
                                      "adamHost1.fabrikam.com:5000",   
                                      "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                      "adamAdmin", "SecretPwd123");  
  
PrincipalSearchResult<AuthenticablePrincipal> oldPrincipals =   
                     AuthenticablePrincipal.FindByLogonTime(ctx,   
                            (DateTime.Now - new TimeSpan(45, 0, 0, 0)),   
                            MatchType.LessThan);  
  
foreach (Principal p in oldPrincipals)  
{  
    p.Delete();  
}  
  
oldPrincipals.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();  
  
```

